reviewText: I Thought my 4 year old grand daughter might like this movie....after watching it maybe 30 times already, she still loves watching it, along with her cousins!
My daughter loved it so much she told me to remember it as a gift idea for her birthday in the summer.
Really awful, watched half. Didn't laugh one time. My son, who is four and loves movies, asked to turn it off. Creepy and strange
Words can not describe how bad this movie is.....not one moment of laughing from my children. Not sure how anyone enjoyed this movie or found it funny
Stay away from this movie. Watching this movie was the biggest waste of time. The worst movie ever! Save your money and stay away.

Creepy, strange, cheap, unwatchable.  Save yourself and your children and steer clear of this one.  The plot is incomprehensible and the characters are unlikeable.  The pirate tie-in is vague at best as most of the story revolves around defeating the giant monkey robot casino.  And I'm not joking.
Cute movie. 5 year old grandson really enjoyed it.  Kept his attention from beginning to end.  Would recommend for kids.
Great movie! Loved it.  My kids adored it. I can't say enough good things about this movie. Fantastic...terrific...spectacular! I would highly recommend it! :-)
